String.Source: I Am Not Experienced Enough For This Sword!
String.Dest: この剣を扱うには経験が足りない！

String.Source: I Am So Close I Can Taste It!
String.Dest: これを試せるようになっているはずだ！

String.Source: I Think I am Getting Very Close Though!
String.Dest: とても近づいているはずだ！

String.Source: I Think I Need A Lot More Practice...
String.Dest: もっと練習が必要だろう…

String.Source: I Think I Am Far Far Away From Wearing This...
String.Dest: これを身につけるには程遠いだろう…
